nodes.text: Phoenix One was a callsign used by Phoenix Squadron, an A-wing squadron that was a part of the early rebellion against the Galactic Empire. A human male flew as Phoenix One at least four years before the Battle of Yavin, during an attack on the Phoenix fleet by Darth Vader.
A pilot bearing the callsign of Phoenix One appeared in Star Wars Rebels: The Siege of Lothal, and was voiced by Matthew Wood.
